headline: 2 Top Stocks to Profit Off the AI and Cryptocurrency Booms
summary: Advanced Micro Devices is positioned for explosive growth in the AI chip market.  Coinbase Global is preparing itself to be a leading financial services platform for the digital economy.  Artificial intelligence (AI) and cryptocurrency are two high-growth markets that offer promising return potential.
